{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">About the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216430/extras/PosterNew.png?t=1737986104\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blue Light is a horror adventure game set in the year 2029. The main character goes in search of his missing sister, exploring the most dangerous and paranormal places in the city.\u00a0The Blue Light game was developed by one person.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game is a study of various locations that are well developed in terms of atmosphere. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game will allow you to interact with both mandatory and optional items for the plot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game will give you a lot of freedom to explore three-dimensional locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game will accompany you with a tense chase, as well as screamers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game contains various references to famous personalities, as well as famous games and movies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Warnings: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game is not recommended for people who suffer from epilepsy or heart disease, as it contains photorealistic models, screamers and flashes of light. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game is dominated by surround sound for a more immersive gaming experience, please play the game with headphones and complete silence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game supports AMD FSR 3.0 technology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game supports ultra-wide resolution (21:9).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Surround sound prevails in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- The game supports English interface and English subtitles.</p>","achievements":{"highlig